comments: Towns (MIN) is already established in a position in Jones' (MEM) path when he turns and absorbs the contact to his side.
Towns (MIN) applies an arm to Morant's (MEM) right arm and chest, affecting his SQBR as he gathers during the driving shot attempt.
Clarke (MEM) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Clarke (MEM) and McDaniels (MIN) engage and disengage while fighting for position during the rebound, and marginal contact occurs.
Towns (MIN) dribbles the ball off of Bane's (MEM) foot and Bane does not intentionally kick it.
Edwards (MIN) places his arm against Clarke (MEM) as he elevates for the rebound, but Clarke loses his balance as a result of the contact with his teammate Morant (MEM).
Russell (MIN) places his forearm against Bane (MEM) and releases from the contact as he steps back.
Brooks (MEM) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
McLaughlin (MIN) commits a take foul on Morant (MEM).
Vanderbilt (MIN) jumps vertically and maintains a legal vertical position contesting the driving shot attempt by Morant (MEM).
